node_1.subject: Sam Moore
node_1.description: Sam Moore received a call from Tao Chiang yesterday and they planned to meet at Hobbs Cafe at 8am on February 14th with Isabella to discuss Sam's mayoral campaign strategy.

node_2.subject: Sam Moore
node_2.description: Sam Moore is looking forward to attending Isabella's Valentine's Day party at Hobbs Cafe tonight. He thinks it will be a great opportunity to meet more voters and share his vision for the Ville.
